    • Method Detail

      • addReminder

        boolean addReminder(java.lang.String pid,
                  java.lang.String preferLanguage,
                  int alertType)
        This will add Reminder for alertType(1 for IVR and 2 for SMS) the patient with uuid:pid. The reminder will be in effect from the next day(midnight).

      • deleteReminder

        boolean deleteReminder(java.lang.String pid,
                     int alertType)
        This will stop sending reminder to the patient with uuid:pid for alert of alertType(1 for IVR and 2 for SMS)
